			<div class="postrow has_after_content">
				
				
				<h2 class="title icon icon0">
					Re: Banning or suspension for Dmitry - community discussion
				</h2>
				

						
						
				<div class="content">
					<div id="post_message_1497766">
						<blockquote class="postcontent restore ">
							Permanent Ban? No.<br />
Suspension? Yes, I'd say at least a month.<br />
Stripped of moderator status? Yes, and I'd say not able to run to become a moderator again, ever.<br />
<br />
Personally, I'd suspend him for a month and put him on probation. If at any time during the probationary period (a year or two) did something similar to this incident that warranted a suspension, a permanent ban.<br />
<br />
A reformation of rules may be in order too, especially as far as sensitivity to certain subjects. I think what dmitry did went overboard, but we should be able to discuss homosexuality and other sensitive subjects to an extent.
						</blockquote>
					</div>

					
				</div>
